          <h3>中国六盘水与美国夏威夷<br>“牵手”同跑马拉松跑步</h3><br>
          <label style="color:#ff6633">中新网2016-05-17 09:25</label>
        </div>
        <div class="list-group auto m-b-sm m-b-lg">
          <img src="<%=GongzhonghaoInfo.URL+"articlePic/article_hot.jpg" %>" style="width:100%" class="list-group-item">
